            . I went up to make the bed on Sunday morning, the prisoner was sitting on the bed, I told the prisoner to get off, he would not.</p>
               <p>Q. Did he lodge there. - A. He had lodged there, but not at that time, I told him three times to get off, the third time he got off the bed; I then found a knife and a steel between the bed and the bolster, he asked me for a hammer, I told him I had no hammer to give him.</p>
